Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好强…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬间…只要一瞬间就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能够打破这个快攻…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果准镜没事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我亲手杀死他们的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.20,0:00:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须承受 并且不断思考这个问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.01,0:00:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我能做的最低限度的赎罪 我现在是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:01:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人现在 正在努力将自己的话付诸实践
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用亲手阻止代表SAO黑暗面的 名为「死枪」的犯罪者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(872,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做到这一点并不是因为桐人很强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是他能够接受自己的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时而烦恼 时而痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是即使如此 仍旧能够继续向前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么…我能做的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:02.97,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\pos(640,543)}幽灵子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续这样出汗的话 会有脱水的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中途下线一次…是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟不管我们在这里说什么 桐人也听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在严重脱水的情况发生之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AmuSphere应该会自动切断游戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 就在观察一阵子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请握住爸爸的手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈的手的温度 一定可以传递到爸爸那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手没办法触及那边的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把我…请连带着我的份也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯的温度 也一定可以传达到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起为爸爸 为桐人加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊桐人 为了那些相信着你的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会永远在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远保护你的身后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支持着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实 是拒绝了知道这家伙名字的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想再次和他们扯上关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 其实这种事本身就是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是强装出一幅已经忘记了的样子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是自欺欺人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得…在讨伐战之前的会议上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙萨！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红眼的沙萨！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条预测线 是诗乃根据她自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:06:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经验 灵感 以及全身斗志所发射的幻影子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后一击 我绝不能辜负她的「幽灵子弹」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有…结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人…不会让你…结束掉这一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 已经结束了 沙萨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的同伙我们也会马上找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「微笑棺木」的杀人行为就此结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(432,670)}Laughing Coffin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该让大会结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「死枪」已经倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(536,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要对你下手的他的同伙也肯定藏匿了踪迹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就算现在登出了应该也没有什么危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防万一 记得马上去报警
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就算我播了110 该怎么解释现状啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的也对…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的委托人好歹也是个公务员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去麻烦下他也不是不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不能在这里问你的真实姓名和住址呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行的 我告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的真名是朝田诗乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住址是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太巧了 我现在潜行的地方就在你附近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么要不我登出之后就去找你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 你愿意…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个值得信任的朋友就住在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我登出了以后就和委托人联系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他派警察过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:10:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别管这个 你就不和我说下你的个人情报？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的真名叫桐谷和人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐谷和人 所以才叫桐人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是很随便的命名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你好意思说我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 为了登出 我们得先把这个BOB做个了断先
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样 诗音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要像昨天那样以决斗来分出高下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这不是已经遍体鳞伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算赢了这样的你 我也一点都不开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜负就留到下次BOB大会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 就让我们结束这场BOB吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定要有一个人HP归零才能决定优胜者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说第一届BOB是两人同时获胜的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因在于 应该获胜的人不小心中了『手榴弹大礼』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手榴弹大礼？那是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然「死枪」的被害者是2人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(547,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 共犯也有2人以上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直蠢爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝田 你在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我啊 朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新川
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 无论如何都想给你庆祝夺冠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买了这个来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 真心恭喜你夺冠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好厉害啊朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗乃 你终于成了GGO最强的枪手了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是朝田的话 终有一天能当上的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝田有着其他人没有的 真正的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝田…你和我说过的吧 会等我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新川…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说了吧 只要我等下去的话 总有一天会属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 所以我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊 这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直陪着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不用依靠那种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会一直…一生保护…你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新…新川
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝田 我喜欢你 我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的诗乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以的哦…朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝田不可以背叛我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新川？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新…川…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以动的哦 朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个注射器里的东西一进入身体的话 肌肉就会无法运动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心肺很快就会停止运转
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注射器？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打了某种药物吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因为我家开医院的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和爸爸也约好了考进医学专业 没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…你就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是另外一个「死枪」？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(763,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…挺厉害啊 看穿了「死枪」的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(769,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错哦 我就是「死枪」的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(687,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这么说 在这次的大赛之前 是我操作Sterben的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 只有今天让我来干现实这边的活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟不能让其他的男人来碰朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是兄弟也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄…兄弟？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前在SAO里加入杀人工会的 是新川的哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 我不会丢下朝田你自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还 还来得及 还能重来的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有去上补习班的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要当医生的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西已经怎么样都行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论父母还是学校那帮人都是无可救药的蠢材！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要能在GGO里当上最强的话就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫ZEXD的人渣 说什么敏系最强的谎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GGO明明是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此我舍弃了现实的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:17:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就杀了ZXED吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 为了让「死枪」成为GGO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(660,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是所有VRMMO中最强的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比他更好的祭品了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 我对这无聊的现实已经毫无眷恋了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起走下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新川…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们一起去像GGO一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更奇幻的也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们在那里得到重生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结为夫妇一起生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起冒险 生孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们成为一体吧 朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 朝田 真美 太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…我的…朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:19:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直…一直都好喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从在学校听说朝田你遇到的那个事件以来 一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能用真的手枪击毙罪犯的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找遍全日本也只有朝田你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过吧 朝田你是真的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以在塑造「死枪」时我选择了54式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(598,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是我憧憬的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你 爱你 比任何人都要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经…什么都不想看到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想感知到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定…不是真实的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.67,0:20:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还让你来救我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你白跑一趟 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆下线后我去找你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他真的过来 也会遭遇危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我已经没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们至今为止只会关注自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会为了自己而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在说这些也许已经太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少在最后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也试着为了他人而战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝…朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝田…朝田…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝田…朝田…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝田…朝田…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:21:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑 诗乃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.90,0:22:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一集 一小步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=========================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:07.97,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}もっと強く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:13.00,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}そう、強くなりたいと願った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.07,0:22:16.69,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,525)}悲しみを超えて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.27,0:22:31.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}変わることない過去に何度も背を向けてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.31,0:22:38.59,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}誰にも見せられない傷を隠したまま ずっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.76,0:22:42.21,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}溢れだしたこの痛みは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.31,0:22:45.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}全て一人で抱きしめる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:48.71,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}いつか消える温もりなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.77,0:22:53.43,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}一つもいらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:56.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}もっと強く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.42,0:23:01.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}そう、強くなりたいと願った
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:07.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}暗闇をかける孤独な星のように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.73,0:23:15.57,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}心深く沈めた弱くて脆い自分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.64,0:23:19.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}言葉にできなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:22.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}声にもならなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.56,0:23:27.69,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}きっと誰にも見つからないように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:32.91,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,825)}ただ 、光を待ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:07.97,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}更加坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:13.00,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}没错 我祈愿能变得更加坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.07,0:22:16.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,525)}去超越悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.27,0:22:31.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}对着一成不变的过去 无数次转过身去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.31,0:22:38.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}藏着无法给任何人看的伤疤 一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.76,0:22:42.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}溢出来的这份伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.31,0:22:45.66,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}全都自己抱着不放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:48.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}如果是终有一天会消失的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.77,0:22:53.43,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}宁肯一个都不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:56.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}更加坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.42,0:23:01.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}没错 我祈愿能变得更加坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:07.66,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}就如同那在黑暗上驰骋的孤独的星尘一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.73,0:23:15.57,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}在内心深处躲避着的脆弱的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.64,0:23:19.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}无法言语
